<actions>
  <update-node tree="member_expression: wallet == firstTrade.buyer.wallet ? NahmiiTypesLib.TradePartyRole.Buyer : NahmiiTypesLib.TradePartyRole.Seller [2634,2744]" label="wallet <= firstTrade.buyer.wallet ? NahmiiTypesLib.TradePartyRole.Buyer : NahmiiTypesLib.TradePartyRole.Seller" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: currencyCt == firstTrade.currencies.intended.ct && currencyId == firstTrade.currencies.intended.id [2356,2454]" label="currencyCt <= firstTrade.currencies.intended.ct || currencyId <= firstTrade.currencies.intended.id" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: currencyCt == lastTrade.currencies.intended.ct && currencyId == lastTrade.currencies.intended.id [2473,2569]" label="currencyCt <= lastTrade.currencies.intended.ct || currencyId <= lastTrade.currencies.intended.id" />
</actions>
